## Approved refactors (scout-informed)
Scouting confirmed: entries are hand-built at **four** append sites in `run_one_try`
(MutationError, general mutation exception, train/eval error, survived-evaluation ‚Äî anchor by
those descriptions, not line numbers); `select_parent` is uniform `_rng.choice` over
`pareto_frontier_try_ids(successful)` with no weight hook; the full `archive` and `try_id` are in
scope at selection and at the write sites; entries already set `parent_try_id` (int) and
`parent_try_ids` (comma-separated str, both parents for combine).

- **R1 ‚Äî `make_entry(...)` factory (approved).** Centralize archive-entry dict construction in
  one factory called at all four append sites. The provenance tag lives INSIDE the factory, so
  the tag is a one-place change now, and every future descriptor (multi-init origin-seed,
  MAP-Elites niche key) is a one-place change later. Factory builds *what* is appended; each exit
  still decides *when*. Failed entries are tagged too (they flow through the same factory) ‚Äî a
  crashed novel attempt is part of "we tried" for the negative-result report.
- **R2 ‚Äî `select_parent` ‚Üí pool / per-candidate weights / weighted draw (approved).** Since G5
  makes it weighted anyway, structure it as: build pool ‚Üí compute weight per candidate ‚Üí weighted
  `_rng` draw. Protection is the first weight term; **crowding distance later lands as another
  term in the same computation** instead of a second rewrite. Signature gains `current_try` +
  archive access (needed for the protection window and off-frontier protected candidates).
- **R3 ‚Äî `parent_try_ids` str‚Üílist (rejected for now).** Combine rule (a) parses the existing
  comma-separated string; not worth touching its consumers in this change.
- **Still deferred (unchanged):** `choose_operation` operator-registry refactor; lineage-graph
  traversal (rung 3); `read_candidate_source` extraction.

## Out of scope
- Per-lineage refinement counting (b), promise-gated protection (e), decay-over-N up-weight ‚Äî
  all graduations, not now.
- Full lineage-graph / genealogy engine ‚Äî build only if MAP-Elites later forces it.
- Hypervolume-per-dollar grading ‚Äî separate project; grace period judged by eye test + the
  negative-result report for now.

